{'Gemini response': '[00:00.000] A Magic Bullet blender sits on a countertop. A man with short dark hair and blue-rimmed glasses leans in, looking intently at something to the right.\n[00:03.000] The man reaches for a bunch of yellow bananas hanging beside a framed picture of a dog.\n[00:05.000] He pulls off a banana and peels it, placing the peeled banana into the empty blender cup. \n[00:07.000] Frozen raspberries are added to the blender cup, followed by more banana slices.\n[00:08.000] The man opens a jar of creamy organic peanut butter. \n[00:11.000] He scoops out a spoonful of peanut butter and adds it to the blender cup. White liquid, likely milk or yogurt, is poured in. \n[00:14.000] Rolled oats are added to the blender cup.\n[00:15.000] The man picks up the blender blade attachment and firmly presses it onto the cup. \n[00:16.000] He places the cup onto the Magic Bullet base and secures it with a twist.\n[00:18.000] He pushes down on the cup to start the blender.\n[00:21.000] He lifts the blender cup from the base and removes the blade attachment.\n[00:22.000]  The man pours the blended smoothie into a clear to-go cup.\n[00:24.000] He takes a sip of the smoothie and smiles. \n'}
