{'Gemini response': '[00:00] A Magic Bullet blender sits on a kitchen counter.  A man with short dark hair and round blue-rimmed glasses peers into the blender cup.\n[00:03] He reaches up and grabs a bunch of ripe bananas hanging from a hook.\n[00:05] He peels a banana and drops slices into the blender cup.\n[00:07] Frozen strawberries are added to the cup.\n[00:08] He scoops peanut butter from a jar.\n[00:11] The peanut butter is added, followed by a generous pour of milk.\n[00:14] He scoops protein powder into the cup.\n[00:15] The man firmly attaches the blender blade to the cup.\n[00:17] He places the cup onto the Magic Bullet base and presses down. The blender whirs to life.\n[00:21] He releases the cup and the blender stops. \n[00:22] He removes the blade attachment and pours the smoothie into a clear plastic to-go cup.\n[00:24] He takes a sip of the smoothie with a satisfied expression.  \n'}
